Date of Accident: 9 July 2026



Triage Only Request



Please find attached our client's images.



Please will you provide an initial assessment to confirm if this vehicle is roadworthy and repairable as soon as possible.  We will forward the official inspection instruction as soon as we are able.



Accident Circumstances:

Our client left their vehicle parked and unattended overnight at their home address on Fairfield Road, Yorkshire. Your insured, in their vehicle has collided into our client's parked vehicle whilst attempting to turn in the road. Our client was made aware of the incident by a witness. Your insured was visiting a neighbour who was approached following the incident and details were obtained.

Damage Description:

Front Offside: Moderate

damage to front offside bumper

Driveable:

Yes



Yours faithfully





